product\/strings\/violin\/GP-10H\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Hill E<\/a><\/u><\/b>: Not as powerful as the other E strings, but is popular for itsvery sweet sound.<\/font><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><font size=\"2\"><b><u><a href=\"https:\/\/www.swstrings.com\/product\/strings\/violin\/GP-550S\" title=\"\" target=\"\">GoldLabel E<\/a><\/u><\/b>: Stronger than the other ThomasticDominant E strings and has a wonderful ringing tone.<\/font><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><font size=\"2\"><b><u><a href=\"https:\/\/www.swstrings.com\/product\/strings\/violin\/GP-J123S\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Jargar E<\/a><\/u><\/b>: Shares qualities similar to the Gold Label E with a rounder, more powerful sound.<\/font><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><font size=\"2\"><b><u><a href=\"https:\/\/www.swstrings.com\/product\/strings\/violin\/GP-L14S\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Larsen E<\/a><\/u><\/b>: Rounds out the Thomastik Dominant A, Dand G helping them sound more like gut strings.<\/font><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><font size=\"2\"><b><u><a href=\"https:\/\/www.swstrings.com\/product\/strings\/violin\/GP-208S\" title=\"\" target=\"\">PirastoOliv E<\/a><\/u><\/b>: The Oliv E is brilliant and powerful especially inhigher positions.<\/font><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in\"><span style=\"font-size: small\"><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>For more E string options, consider the <u><a href=\"https:\/\/www.swstrings.com\/product\/strings\/violin\/GP-D129\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Dominant &#8220;no E&#8221; set<\/a><\/u> to mix and match to your preference.<\/p>","on_sale":false,"prices":{"price":"7578","regular_price":"7578","sale_price":"7578","price_range":{"min_amount":"7578","max_amount":"9453"},"currency_code":"USD","currency_symbol":"$","currency_minor_unit":2,"currency_decimal_separator":".","currency_thousand_separator":",","currency_pref